OverCrank is a Chome extension designed to display and visualize the inner workings of the Qwik Web Framework. This is done by capturing the lazy loaded network requests and interpreting the resumability model which is embedded within the HTML of all Qwik websites.

OverCrank targets Qwik development websites built in development mode using the standard 'npm run dev' build flow. Instructions for getting a Qwik page up and running to test can be found at https://qwik.builder.io/docs/getting-started/ .
